fields.Title: WHIRLING F3 ORB / love did him in
fields.Placement: on the whirling roof around klaasje and everywhere

fields.Title: Drama: "Gone forever... Sire, thee shall ne..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Gone forever... Sire, thee shall never findeth another mistress quaint like her!

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "You do not know. A wind of needles...."
fields.Dialogue Text: You do not know. A wind of needles. Airships flutter in the stratosphere.

fields.Title: Volition: "It appears this one has *not* been..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It appears this one has *not* been entirely corrupted... this may help. This may help the others see.

fields.Title: You: "How do I... know all this then?"
fields.Dialogue Text: How do I... know all this then?

fields.Title: You: ""Why?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why?"

fields.Title: You: ""Was it? Real?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Was it? Real?"

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["whirling.sense_inland_klaasje_second"]  and  Variable["TASK.arrest_klaasje_done"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.enter_cavern_done"] == false  and  IsHourBetween(7, 22) == true

fields.Title: You: "I already miss Klaasje."
fields.Dialogue Text: I already miss Klaasje.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Feels good, doesn't it? Doing the r..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Feels good, doesn't it? Doing the right thing.

fields.Title: Empathy: "Real as anything."
fields.Dialogue Text: Real as anything.

fields.Title: You: "What is communism in this?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What is communism in this?

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "If it weren't for her he would not..."
fields.Dialogue Text: If it weren't for her he would not have been there. The shot would not have connected with his soft palate...

fields.Title: You: "(Turn to Klaasje.) "Looks like love..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Turn to Klaasje.) "Looks like love did him in after all."

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["whirling.klaasje_love_did_in_said"]  and  Variable["TASK.arrest_klaasje_done"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.enter_cavern_done"] == false  and  IsHourBetween(7, 22) == true

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "As you look back you think: So love..."
fields.Dialogue Text: As you look back you think: So love did *do him in* after all.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Who knows?... It's getting cold out..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Who knows?... It's getting cold out. You should go.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Or was it communism that killed him..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Or was it communism that killed him and love that did him in...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I don't know..." She looks down at..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know..." She looks down at the yard -- then back into her coffee.

fields.Title: You: "[Finish thought.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Finish thought.]

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "No. Communism killed him, remember?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No. Communism killed him, remember? Love made it possible. You know this much.

fields.Title: You: "Say nothing. Let her answer."
fields.Dialogue Text: Say nothing. Let her answer.

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["whirling.sense_inland_klaasje_first"]  and  Variable["TASK.arrest_klaasje_done"] == false  and  Variable["TASK.enter_cavern_done"] == false  and  IsHourBetween(7, 22) == true

fields.Title: Authority: "Hey, what is this funeral vibe here..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hey, what is this funeral vibe here? You did what any good cop would do. Pat yourself on the back and move on.

fields.Title: You: "[Discard thought.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Discard thought.]

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "If it weren't for her he would not..."
fields.Dialogue Text: If it weren't for her he would not have been there. The shot would not have connected with his soft palate...

fields.Title: You: "I was right..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I was right...

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "She's silent, holding on to her cof..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She's silent, holding on to her coffee mug. No vapour rises from it -- it's cold.

fields.Title: Volition: "You were just being a good cop."
fields.Dialogue Text: You were just being a good cop.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Yeah..." she finally breaks the si..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah..." she finally breaks the silence. "I'd like to think he didn't *love* me. Or that it was chemically-induced and not real."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Of course you do, Harry. Everyone d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of course you do, Harry. Everyone does.

fields.Title: You: "It *killed* him... (Look at Klaasje..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It *killed* him... (Look at Klaasje.)

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Easier that way." She takes a sip."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Easier that way." She takes a sip.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Remember this silence. The lady is..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Remember this silence. The lady is dangerous. People suffer around her.

fields.Title: Half Light: "You fool! What are you waiting for?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You fool! What are you waiting for?! Mount a rescue operation and go get her back!
